---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>

  <Hero />

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="about reveal" id="about">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-label">關於我</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">從識別到介面，從程式到電路。</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>視覺／UI 設計專長的資訊管理學系應屆畢業生，能從品牌識別、海報、App 介面一路做到前端與硬體實作。</p>
          <p>曾主導兩項獲獎產品專題，從 0 到 1 完成設計、開發與上架，並長期擔任校內活動的美宣與攝影。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-status"><span class="pulse"></span>目前同時求職與自由接案中</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-aside">
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="num">2</div><div class="lab">獲獎產品專題主導</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="num">16<span style="font-size:1.4rem"> 萬</span></div><div class="lab">創業補助金額</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="num">0→1</div><div class="lab">設計・開發・上架全包</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="num">3+</div><div class="lab">年校內活動美宣攝影</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Works -->
  <section class="works" id="works">
    <div class="section-head works-head reveal">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">精選作品</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">每個專案，從 0 到 1。</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="https://cake.me/portfolios/3d42da" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">完整作品集 ↗</a>
    </div>

    <div class="works-grid">

      <!-- Work 1 -->
      <article class="work reveal">
        <div class="work-visual">
          <div class="work-index">01</div>
          <div class="slot-bg" style="--tint: rgba(108,140,255,0.14)"></div>
          <image-slot id="work-longzaiying" shape="rect" placeholder="拖入 攏災影 App 截圖／主視覺"></image-slot>
        </div>
        <div class="work-body">
          <div class="work-role">防災避難 App · <b>美術宣傳負責人</b> · 大三–至今</div>
          <h3 class="work-title">攏災影</h3>
          <p class="work-sub">App UI、品牌識別、Logo 與吉祥物設計，以及宣傳影片製作。</p>
          <div class="work-metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="mv"><em>16</em> 萬</div><div class="ml">創業補助</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="mv"><em>114</em> 年度</div><div class="ml">實戰模擬平台入選團隊</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="award-row">
            <span class="award">第二梯次 大專院校實戰模擬平台</span>
            <span class="award">創業補助 16 萬元</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="work-points">
            <li>負責 App UI 設計（Figma）與品牌識別，設計 Logo 與吉祥物。</li>
            <li>製作並剪輯品牌宣傳短片、經營產品社群平台。</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="work-tags">
            <span class="tag">Figma</span>
            <span class="tag">Illustrator</span>
            <span class="tag">Clip Studio Paint</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Work 2 -->
      <article class="work reveal">
        <div class="work-visual">
          <div class="work-index">02</div>
          <div class="slot-bg" style="--tint: rgba(77,240,150,0.14)"></div>
          <image-slot id="work-dayday" shape="rect" placeholder="拖入 DayDay 補給站 杯墊／App 截圖"></image-slot>
        </div>
        <div class="work-body">
          <div class="work-role">AIoT 智慧杯墊專題 · <b>裝置開發與視覺設計負責人</b> · 大四</div>
          <h3 class="work-title">DayDay 補給站</h3>
          <p class="work-sub">智慧杯墊從概念到成品，3D 建模、硬體開發與配套 App 一手包辦。</p>
          <div class="work-metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="mv"><em>第 5</em> 名</div><div class="ml">系展 15 組中</div></div>
            <div class="metric"><div class="mv">Google Play</div><div class="ml">App 已上架封測</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="award-row">
            <span class="award">系展 15 組第 5 名</span>
            <span class="award">Google Play 封測上架</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="work-points">
            <li>主導智慧杯墊從概念到成品，完成原型 3D 建模與硬體開發。</li>
            <li>設計並開發配套 App，Figma 製作 UI、React Native 實作介面。</li>
            <li>包辦專題識別與宣傳（Logo、海報設計）。</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="work-tags">
            <span class="tag">Blender</span>
            <span class="tag">Fusion</span>
            <span class="tag">樹莓派 Pico W</span>
            <span class="tag">Figma</span>
            <span class="tag">React Native</span>
            <span class="tag">Illustrator</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Work 3 -->
      <article class="work reveal">
        <div class="work-visual">
          <div class="work-index">03</div>
          <div class="slot-bg" style="--tint: var(--accent-wash)"></div>
          <image-slot id="work-langcenter" shape="rect" placeholder="拖入 語言中心網頁截圖"></image-slot>
        </div>
        <div class="work-body">
          <div class="work-role">校內語言中心 · <b>網頁重構工讀生</b> · 大三</div>
          <h3 class="work-title">語言中心網頁重構</h3>
          <p class="work-sub">以前端技術優化介面，並協助建置中、英文雙語網頁。</p>
          <div class="work-metrics">
            <div class="metric"><div class="mv"><em>中・英</em></div><div class="ml">雙語網頁建置</div></div>
          </div>
          <ul class="work-points">
            <li>以 HTML／CSS／JavaScript 優化校內語言中心網頁介面。</li>
            <li>協助建置中、英文雙語網頁。</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="work-tags">
            <span class="tag">HTML</span>
            <span class="tag">CSS</span>
            <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience -->
  <section class="reveal" id="experience">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-label">設計與活動經歷</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">在校園裡，把作品做進真實場景。</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-dot"></div>
        <div class="tl-when">大一–大二</div>
        <div class="tl-title">紫荊書院　數位媒體部幹部</div>
        <div class="tl-role">美編・攝影・主持</div>
        <div class="tl-desc">第五屆院刊美編，以 InDesign 完成四篇專欄排版並赴嘉義 2 間獨立書店募資；負責院友回娘家、生涯知能課程、第 16 屆迎新等多場活動之主視覺、美宣與攝影，並擔任主持。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-dot"></div>
        <div class="tl-when">大二上</div>
        <div class="tl-title">系學會　美宣長</div>
        <div class="tl-role">視覺設計</div>
        <div class="tl-desc">設計新生資訊圖文與系服宣傳素材（Canva）。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-dot"></div>
        <div class="tl-when">大二上</div>
        <div class="tl-title">三系聯合宿營（資管・犯防・哲學）　美宣組</div>
        <div class="tl-role">視覺設計・活動攝影</div>
        <div class="tl-desc">設計活動 Logo、製作大地遊戲道具並擔任活動攝影。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills -->
  <section class="reveal" id="skills">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-label">技能</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">設計、開發、硬體，一條龍。</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>視覺設計</h4>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Illustrator</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">InDesign</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Clip Studio Paint</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Canva</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>UI 設計</h4>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Figma</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>開發</h4>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">HTML</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">CSS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">React Native</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>3D ・ 硬體</h4>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Blender</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Fusion</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">樹莓派 Pico W</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>影像</h4>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">活動攝影</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">短片拍攝與剪輯</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>語言 ・ 軟實力</h4>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">中文（母語）</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">團隊溝通協作</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">危機應變</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Education -->
  <section class="reveal" id="education">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-label">學歷與證照</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">學術根基。</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="edu-grid">
      <div class="edu-card">
        <div class="edu-kind">學歷</div>
        <div class="edu-name">國立中正大學　資訊管理學系</div>
        <div class="edu-meta">2022.09 – 2026.12（預計）<br />跨校修習雲林科技大學設計課程</div>
      </div>
      <div class="edu-card">
        <div class="edu-kind">證照</div>
        <div class="edu-name">色彩規劃管理師　初級能力鑑定</div>
        <div class="edu-meta">經濟部產業發展署<br />2026.01</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="contact reveal" id="contact">
    <div class="section-label" style="display:inline-block">聯繫</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">有專案想法？讓我們聊聊。</h2>
    <p class="contact-lead">無論是全職機會、設計合作或自由接案，都歡迎來信。</p>
    <div class="contact-links">
      <a href="mailto:xlin9857@gmail.com" class="contact-link">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
        xlin9857@gmail.com
      </a>
      <a href="tel:0900782414" class="contact-link">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92Z"/></svg>
        0900 782 414
      </a>
      <a href="https://cake.me/portfolios/3d42da" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg>
        作品集
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/XinEnLin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12Z"/></svg>
        GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline src="/image-slot.js"></script>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Section separators */
  section + section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* ── About ── */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .about-text p + p { margin-top: 1.4rem; }

  .about-aside { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }

  /* ── Featured Works ── */
  .works-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .works-head .section-title { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .works-grid { display: grid; gap: 2.5rem; }

  .work {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--surface-card);
    transition: all var(--dur-med) ease;
  }

  .work:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(var(--lift-md));
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
  }

  .work:nth-child(even) .work-visual { order: 2; }

  .work-visual {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 360px;
  }

  .work-visual image-slot {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .slot-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, var(--tint) 0 12px, transparent 12px 24px),
      var(--surface-card-hover);
  }

  .work-index {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.4rem;
    left: 1.6rem;
    z-index: 3;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--nav-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    width: 2.6rem;
    height: 2.6rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .work-body {
    padding: 2.4rem 2.6rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .work-role {
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .work-role b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: var(--weight-medium); }

  .work-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }

  .work-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  .work-metrics {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .metric .mv {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .metric .mv em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .metric .ml {
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .award-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  .award {
    font-size: var(--text-3xs);
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-wash);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  }

  .work-points {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.55rem;
  }

  .work-points li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .work-points li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.65em;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .work-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 0.6rem;
  }

  .work-tags .tag {
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    transition: all var(--dur-fast);
  }

  .work:hover .work-tags .tag { border-color: var(--border-strong); }

  /* ── Experience Timeline ── */
  .timeline { max-width: var(--measure-timeline); }

  .tl-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2.2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.4rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tl-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }

  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -5px;
    top: 4px;
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-dot-glow);
  }

  .tl-when {
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .tl-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-title-sm);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .tl-role {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .tl-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  /* ── Skills ── */
  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.4rem 2.4rem;
  }

  .skill-group h4 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .skill-group .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  /* ── Education ── */
  .edu-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.4rem;
  }

  .edu-card {
    padding: 2rem;
